1
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:50,359
In my memory,

2
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:52,359
Dad could do anything.

3
00:00:55,880 --> 00:00:57,079
On the pitch,

4
00:00:57,159 --> 00:00:59,520
he taught so many kids how to play.

5
00:01:00,119 --> 00:01:00,920
But yesterday,

6
00:01:01,359 --> 00:01:03,560
for the first time, I sat in the stands

7
00:01:03,640 --> 00:01:04,920
and watched Dad's game.

8
00:01:05,359 --> 00:01:06,280
That's when I realized

9
00:01:06,560 --> 00:01:07,879
Dad has gotten old.

10
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:09,799
He couldn't outplay the others,

11
00:01:09,959 --> 00:01:11,359
couldn't outrun them either.

12
00:01:11,799 --> 00:01:13,920
But he kept running with all his might,

13
00:01:14,560 --> 00:01:16,280
and never once gave up.

14
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:18,239
So Dad isn't Superman after all.

15
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:19,920
But it's this very Dad

16
00:01:20,280 --> 00:01:21,959
who taught me what true strength is.

17
00:01:22,519 --> 00:01:23,799
It's not about being able to do everything,

18
00:01:24,239 --> 00:01:25,519
but about facing hardship

19
00:01:25,719 --> 00:01:27,239
with a spirit that never surrenders.

20
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:28,159
Dad,

21
00:01:28,359 --> 00:01:29,439
you're my pride,

22
00:01:29,640 --> 00:01:30,680
you're my hero.

23
00:01:32,319 --> 00:01:33,959
Look at your daughter, so thoughtful.

24
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:35,200
It's really touching.

25
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:39,480
How am I already old?

26
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:41,000
I'm only in my early thirties.

27
00:01:42,359 --> 00:01:43,840
My girl says I can't outplay others.

28
00:01:44,079 --> 00:01:45,280
If I don't win one more game,

29
00:01:45,959 --> 00:01:46,560
from now on in this house,

30
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:47,719
I won't be able to show my face.

31
00:01:48,159 --> 00:01:49,040
Oh, come on now.

32
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,400
He hasn't been able to pull off a win,

33
00:01:57,599 --> 00:01:59,280
so he's bottling up all his frustration.

34
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:01,120
Just don't hold it against him.

35
00:02:01,959 --> 00:02:02,680
Auntie,

36
00:02:03,079 --> 00:02:05,040
I just feel he tells me nothing.

37
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:06,319
Like I'm an outsider.

38
00:02:07,359 --> 00:02:09,159
Lately, when he comes to the shop,

39
00:02:09,319 --> 00:02:10,840
the mood is so heavy

40
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:12,560
I don't even dare talk to him.

41
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:14,240
And he doesn't talk to me either.

42
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:16,639
So, is he treating me like an outsider too?

43
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:19,240
Auntie, that's not what I meant.

44
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:21,560
This one looks pretty nice.

45
00:02:21,639 --> 00:02:22,560
Excuse me, could I get a bag?

46
00:02:22,879 --> 00:02:23,520
Sure, thanks.

47
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:25,879
That guy,

48
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:27,599
he's just too hot-headed.

49
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:28,199
I

50
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:29,439
really need to set him straight.

51
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:30,599
Tell you what,

52
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:31,280
in the next couple of days,

53
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,280
the two of you together,

54
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:33,039
come over for dinner.

55
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:34,280
If you wanna scold him,

56
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:35,159
I'll help you do it.

57
00:02:37,159 --> 00:02:37,759
Auntie,

58
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:39,400
I'd better just leave him alone.

59
00:02:39,599 --> 00:02:40,479
Otherwise later,

60
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:41,639
he'll say I'm distracting him again.

61
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:42,840
Boss lady,

62
00:02:42,879 --> 00:02:43,960
Weigh this, please. How much is it?

63
00:02:44,319 --> 00:02:45,039
Xiaoyong's mom,

64
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:45,560
This one here,

65
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:46,479
it's on the house.

66
00:02:47,199 --> 00:02:47,680
No, I can't accept that.

67
00:02:47,919 --> 00:02:49,120
What are you doing? Come on.

68
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:50,400
It's fine, really.

69
00:02:50,439 --> 00:02:50,960
Here, take it.

70
00:02:51,080 --> 00:02:52,000
Xiaoyong right now

71
00:02:52,039 --> 00:02:53,639
is fighting for Changzhou's honor.

72
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:54,840
Out there playing,

73
00:02:54,879 --> 00:02:55,960
working so hard on the pitch.

74
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:57,360
I watched the game.

75
00:02:57,599 --> 00:02:58,319
That kid

76
00:02:58,439 --> 00:02:59,960
didn't let us Changzhou folks down.

77
00:03:00,479 --> 00:03:01,520
So this is a gift for him.

78
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,840
That's a separate matter.

79
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:03,479
I can't.

80
00:03:04,199 --> 00:03:05,120
No need to be so polite.

81
00:03:05,159 --> 00:03:05,520
Come on, take it.

82
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:06,599
Xiaoyong's mom, listen.

83
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:07,280
Here, come here.

84
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,919
This fish is the freshest one.

85
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:09,680
Take it home

86
00:03:09,879 --> 00:03:10,800
for Xiaoyong.

87
00:03:11,039 --> 00:03:12,199
Makes the most nourishing soup.

88
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:13,719
He's out there for all of Changzhou,

89
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:15,280
working so hard, giving his all.

90
00:03:15,639 --> 00:03:16,240
And this too.

91
00:03:16,479 --> 00:03:17,080
This one as well.

92
00:03:17,599 --> 00:03:18,280
And this, and this.

93
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:18,840
No, no, I can't.

94
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:19,439
Really, no.

95
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:21,560
We've got all this at home.

96
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:22,879
Just take it.

97
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:23,879
On the football pitch,

98
00:03:23,919 --> 00:03:24,919
we can't really help.

99
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:25,639
But off the pitch,

100
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:26,800
can't we at least get the kid

101
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:27,520
an extra dish or two?

102
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:28,599
Exactly, exactly.

103
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:29,199
Here.

104
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:29,800
This one too.

105
00:03:29,919 --> 00:03:30,639
This is for you as well.

106
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:32,039
This one,

107
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,280
stewed with pork ribs in soup,

108
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:34,840
is incredibly nourishing.

109
00:03:35,439 --> 00:03:36,680
Auntie, look,

110
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:37,840
next time,

111
00:03:38,039 --> 00:03:39,280
if we manage to get tickets,

112
00:03:39,319 --> 00:03:40,479
we'll go cheer Changzhou FC on

113
00:03:40,599 --> 00:03:41,039
in person.

114
00:03:41,199 --> 00:03:42,319
Go root for Changzhou FC.

115
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:45,360
The kid didn't win the match.

116
00:03:45,759 --> 00:03:47,080
He really let us down.

117
00:03:47,479 --> 00:03:48,280
I feel a bit embarrassed.

118
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:50,599
He did us proud, absolutely.

119
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:52,120
It was a friendly match.

120
00:03:52,319 --> 00:03:53,719
Winning isn't the main thing.

121
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:54,840
What matters most

122
00:03:54,919 --> 00:03:56,280
is that Xiaoyong and the team showed

123
00:03:56,319 --> 00:03:58,120
Changzhou's fighting spirit.

124
00:03:58,280 --> 00:03:58,759
Besides,

125
00:03:58,960 --> 00:03:59,759
after eating my fish,

126
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:01,800
they're bound to win next time.

127
00:04:01,919 --> 00:04:02,919
They'll definitely win.

128
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,280
You're all being way too kind.

129
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:04,680
Well then,

130
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:05,520
thank you so much.

131
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,840
Here, here, take it, take it.

132
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:07,759
Thank you all, thank you.

133
00:04:07,759 --> 00:04:08,120
Thanks.

134
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:08,759
Take all of it.

135
00:04:09,439 --> 00:04:10,280
Everyone, quiet down a moment.

136
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:12,639
I've got two things to say.

137
00:04:12,919 --> 00:04:13,479
First,

138
00:04:13,599 --> 00:04:14,919
the city leaders are taking

139
00:04:14,919 --> 00:04:16,079
Changzhou FC's current situation

140
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:17,199
very seriously.

141
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:18,240
Today,

142
00:04:18,759 --> 00:04:20,480
they've issued us a call-up order.

143
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:21,600
Every player,

144
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:23,040
take this recruitment order

145
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:23,720
back to your workplace later,

146
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:25,399
and apply for leave with your employers.

147
00:04:25,519 --> 00:04:26,519
For the coming period,

148
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:27,839
we're doing intensive training.

149
00:04:28,399 --> 00:04:30,240
We're the focus of the whole city now.

150
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:32,759
The whole city's counting on Changzhou FC

151
00:04:32,879 --> 00:04:33,720
to make them proud.

152
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,000
So whatever work you've got,

153
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:35,560
set it aside.

154
00:04:35,839 --> 00:04:36,680
Starting tomorrow,

155
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:37,920
we're in full closed-door training.

156
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:41,120
Now, for the second thing.

157
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:43,240
A lot of people have been saying

158
00:04:44,959 --> 00:04:47,480
that Changzhou FC hasn't scored a goal yet

159
00:04:47,879 --> 00:04:49,000
because of me,

160
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:50,279
the team leader,

161
00:04:50,639 --> 00:04:52,040
and my unlucky name.

162
00:04:52,399 --> 00:04:53,360
So I thought about it.

163
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:55,079
My name is Liu Jinling,

164
00:04:56,079 --> 00:04:57,480
which sounds like "zero goals."

165
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:58,800
So yesterday,

166
00:04:58,839 --> 00:04:59,879
I went down to the police station.

167
00:05:00,199 --> 00:05:01,279
I solemnly announce:

168
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:02,639
from this day forward,

169
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,399
my name is Liu Changjin.

170
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:06,399
Great, great, great!

171
00:05:08,439 --> 00:05:10,360
Let's not let everyone down!

172
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:11,720
Train hard,

173
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:12,759
and score lots of goals!

174
00:05:13,439 --> 00:05:15,160
I mean, I'm "Liu Changjin" now!

175
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,879
Great, great, great!

176
00:05:24,319 --> 00:05:24,879
No wonder.

177
00:05:24,879 --> 00:05:26,120
That player looked so familiar.

178
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:27,120
It was you, kid!

179
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:28,839
I had no idea you had it in you.

180
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:29,800
What are you still doing here,

181
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:30,839
working as a Dragon Tamer?

182
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:31,519
Get going!

183
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:32,920
You have my full support.

184
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:33,800
Full pay, as usual.

185
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:35,279
Train hard,

186
00:05:35,639 --> 00:05:36,639
and represent our Dinosaur Park.

187
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:37,519
Show them

188
00:05:37,639 --> 00:05:38,399
what a real

189
00:05:38,399 --> 00:05:39,160
Changzhou's T-Rex looks like!

190
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:43,800
Mr. Zhang.

191
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:45,519
From now on, my classes

192
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,319
will be in your hands.

193
00:05:46,399 --> 00:05:47,079
Thank you.

194
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:48,279
Don't be so polite with me.

195
00:05:49,319 --> 00:05:49,879
Honestly,

196
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:51,360
I wish I could play in your place.

197
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:52,680
Thank you, Coach.

198
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:54,839
When are you gonna score a goal?

199
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:55,519
Yeah,

200
00:05:55,519 --> 00:05:56,519
when are we

201
00:05:56,519 --> 00:05:57,879
gonna win a match?

202
00:05:58,360 --> 00:06:00,920
We're gonna win one!

203
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,160
Win one!

204
00:06:02,199 --> 00:06:03,759
The coach is working on it too, right?

205
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:04,839
You guys train hard.

206
00:06:05,199 --> 00:06:06,319
We're counting on you in the future.

207
00:06:09,079 --> 00:06:10,040
Come on, back to training.

208
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,199
Now go and train hard.

209
00:06:13,639 --> 00:06:14,600
You've got to keep up

210
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:15,439
this fighting spirit.

211
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:16,360
For the next match,

212
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:17,720
I'll bring my friends from Europe

213
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:18,560
to watch together.

214
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:19,680
Please, Boss, don't!

215
00:06:19,879 --> 00:06:21,040
Look how badly we've been losing.

216
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,120
Don't make us a laughingstock.

217
00:06:22,279 --> 00:06:23,120
What's there to be afraid of?

218
00:06:23,519 --> 00:06:24,240
Let me tell you,

219
00:06:24,399 --> 00:06:25,759
winning or losing really doesn't matter.

220
00:06:26,079 --> 00:06:27,399
What matters is the attitude.

221
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:29,319
I mean, you rascal,

222
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:31,800
pulling off something this big on the sly,

223
00:06:31,879 --> 00:06:33,160
and not telling the company sooner.

224
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:35,399
If I'd known you were in the Jiangsu Super League,

225
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:37,079
I'd not only excuse you from work,

226
00:06:37,399 --> 00:06:39,120
I'd drive you to training myself!

227
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:40,759
Thank you, Boss.

228
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,040
Over here.

229
00:06:53,279 --> 00:06:54,360
Silver noodles with shrimp balls.

230
00:06:55,839 --> 00:06:56,759
Winning Combo.

231
00:06:59,040 --> 00:06:59,920
Fried dough sticks and eggs.

232
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,600
One-Nil Combo.

233
00:07:04,439 --> 00:07:05,000
Steamed buns.

234
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:08,240
Guaranteed-Win Combo.

235
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:10,759
What's up, Mom?

236
00:07:12,519 --> 00:07:14,240
What's all this you've got going on?

237
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:15,399
Oh, this?

238
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:17,480
The regulars suggested it.

239
00:07:17,879 --> 00:07:18,959
They said the combos

240
00:07:19,079 --> 00:07:20,439
should have lucky names.

241
00:07:20,879 --> 00:07:22,360
Every day I keep wishing

242
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:23,040
that you guys

243
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:24,399
will win a match.

244
00:07:29,639 --> 00:07:30,079
Mom.

245
00:07:30,879 --> 00:07:32,079
I'll be away for a few days.

246
00:07:32,399 --> 00:07:33,160
Team training camp.

247
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:34,920
So I can't come help out.

248
00:07:35,079 --> 00:07:35,639
Okay, okay.

249
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:37,040
Oh, by the way.

250
00:07:37,879 --> 00:07:39,360
Did you have a fight with Yaoyao?

251
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:41,120
No.

252
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:42,439
Nothing like that.

253
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:43,600
Just been busy lately.

254
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:44,920
That's all.

255
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,120
Yaoyao is a good girl.

256
00:07:46,279 --> 00:07:47,079
She's sincere.

257
00:07:47,199 --> 00:07:48,480
And she truly cares about you.

258
00:07:48,879 --> 00:07:50,240
Don't let her down.

259
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:53,399
Mom.

260
00:07:53,399 --> 00:07:54,480
I know all that.

261
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:55,680
Good.

262
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:56,839
But look at the mess

263
00:07:56,839 --> 00:07:57,959
I've made of my life.

264
00:07:59,079 --> 00:07:59,920
About the money,

265
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:01,160
don't you worry.

266
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:02,560
All these years,

267
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:03,600
running this shop,

268
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,000
I've saved up enough

269
00:08:05,199 --> 00:08:06,560
for your wedding.

270
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,199
This much.

271
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:15,399
Eight hundred thousand.

272
00:08:19,079 --> 00:08:19,600
Mom.

273
00:08:21,439 --> 00:08:22,199
Xiaoyong.

274
00:08:22,759 --> 00:08:24,000
Mom doesn't want anything else.

275
00:08:24,399 --> 00:08:25,519
I just hope you two

276
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:27,160
can live peacefully

277
00:08:27,519 --> 00:08:29,000
and happily.

278
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:31,680
Sister Fang.

279
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:33,600
Give me a Champion's Combo.

280
00:08:33,639 --> 00:08:34,000
Coming right up.

281
00:08:34,519 --> 00:08:35,120
Xiaoyong.

282
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,200
In the next match,

283
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:36,919
you play your best out there.

284
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:38,120
The whole family's behind you.

285
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:39,200
Go get 'em.

286
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:44,480
Mom.

287
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,639
You're pretty bold with that name.

288
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:48,519
In Mom's heart,

289
00:08:48,919 --> 00:08:49,440
you

290
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:51,919
will always be a champion.

291
00:08:57,639 --> 00:08:58,279
I'm off, Mom.

292
00:08:58,960 --> 00:08:59,320
Okay.

293
00:08:59,679 --> 00:09:00,360
Take care, son.

294
00:09:35,279 --> 00:09:36,440
Out here this late at night,

295
00:09:36,559 --> 00:09:37,399
working so hard?

296
00:09:40,799 --> 00:09:41,759
If I don't train harder,

297
00:09:42,799 --> 00:09:44,480
I'll lose the shirt off my back.

298
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:46,600
One more.

299
00:09:50,679 --> 00:09:52,200
This "city hero" title,

300
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:54,000
I can't carry it.

301
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,200
If we don't win one game,

302
00:09:57,279 --> 00:09:58,639
I'm gonna have to emigrate.

303
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:00,840
Emigrate, huh?

304
00:10:01,519 --> 00:10:02,279
Come on, tell me,

305
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:03,159
where do you want to move to?

306
00:10:05,399 --> 00:10:06,159
Nantong.

307
00:10:06,559 --> 00:10:07,279
Nantong?

308
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,039
You little punk.

309
00:10:09,039 --> 00:10:10,440
You're defecting on us?

310
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:15,240
I mean,

311
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:17,679
when have we ever been humiliated like this?

312
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:19,200
If I were a few years younger,

313
00:10:19,559 --> 00:10:20,720
wouldn't I have scored already?

314
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:23,600
Look at me.

315
00:10:25,399 --> 00:10:26,559
The iron gate of defense,

316
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:28,879
all rusted out.

317
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:30,080
And you,

318
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:31,399
your golden right foot,

319
00:10:31,519 --> 00:10:32,159
it's broken.

320
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:33,759
You kid,

321
00:10:33,919 --> 00:10:35,600
do you remember when you were little,

322
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:36,799
you pointed at Old Chang and said,

323
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:37,919
"You'll regret this.

324
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:40,080
I'll lead China out of Asia

325
00:10:40,279 --> 00:10:41,039
and win the World Cup."

326
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:43,200
We can't win the World Cup,

327
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:46,919
but the Jiangsu Super League,

328
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:49,600
we can win one game, right?

329
00:10:50,799 --> 00:10:52,039
Our childhood dreams,

330
00:10:52,799 --> 00:10:53,960
we should fulfill at least one.

331
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:01,960
It has to be this summer.

332
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:04,919
Bro,

333
00:11:05,879 --> 00:11:06,480
did you see the trending topics?

334
00:11:06,639 --> 00:11:07,120
What trending topics?

335
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,159
Our game against Nanjing

336
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:09,960
is trending.

337
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:10,919
We lost the match,

338
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:12,399
but the audience seems to like us.

339
00:11:12,639 --> 00:11:13,480
They're calling us Thirteen-Nil.

340
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,240
Don't you find it humiliating?

341
00:11:17,519 --> 00:11:17,879
Humiliating?

342
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:19,519
What's humiliating about it?

343
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,679
Winning and losing is normal, isn't it?

344
00:11:26,399 --> 00:11:27,399
We've got training tomorrow morning.

345
00:11:27,879 --> 00:11:29,120
Get some sleep. Good night.

346
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:07,679
Our company,

347
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:09,120
not bad, huh?

348
00:13:10,320 --> 00:13:10,759
Impressive.

349
00:13:11,559 --> 00:13:13,039
Pleasure doing business with your company.

350
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:15,039
Do you have time tomorrow?

351
00:13:15,399 --> 00:13:17,039
I'd like to invite you to watch

352
00:13:17,120 --> 00:13:18,399
a Changzhou FC football match.

353
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:20,200
Old Ma,

354
00:13:20,720 --> 00:13:21,519
everyone says

355
00:13:21,559 --> 00:13:23,159
watching Chinese football is frustrating.

356
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:24,320
Why don't you take me

357
00:13:24,320 --> 00:13:25,480
to try some Changzhou cuisine instead.

358
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:27,639
When you get to Europe,

359
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:28,840
I'll take you to the Champions League.

360
00:13:29,919 --> 00:13:30,720
Our Jiangsu Super League

361
00:13:30,799 --> 00:13:32,320
is way better than the Champions League.

362
00:13:33,440 --> 00:13:34,840
You should go to a European stadium

363
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:37,159
and experience the Champions League first.

364
00:13:37,879 --> 00:13:39,840
That's real football.

365
00:13:41,240 --> 00:13:42,679
Alright, I'll take you to watch it tomorrow.

366
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:46,879
Huai'an FC is also one of

367
00:13:46,879 --> 00:13:47,840
the highlights of this Jiangsu Super League.

368
00:13:48,039 --> 00:13:49,679
Fans call this team

369
00:13:49,679 --> 00:13:50,440
the "Wave-Riding Stallion,"

370
00:13:50,600 --> 00:13:51,960
giving off a real knight-errant vibe.

371
00:13:52,159 --> 00:13:53,039
This Huai'an FC

372
00:13:53,039 --> 00:13:55,440
is jokingly called a Robin Hood squad online.

373
00:13:55,639 --> 00:13:57,559
Never lost against southern Jiangsu teams,

374
00:13:57,720 --> 00:13:59,879
never won against northern Jiangsu teams.

375
00:14:00,240 --> 00:14:01,159
I wonder today,

376
00:14:01,159 --> 00:14:03,759
as the league's two biggest draws meet,

377
00:14:03,919 --> 00:14:06,120
what kind of sparks will fly.

378
00:14:15,279 --> 00:14:17,279
Go, go, go, push to the middle!

379
00:14:17,559 --> 00:14:18,639
Keep up, keep up, keep up!

380
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:32,039
Let's go!

381
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:34,120
Let's go!

382
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:35,960
Let's go!

383
00:14:36,679 --> 00:14:37,679
Let's go!

384
00:14:38,480 --> 00:14:39,279
Changzhou!

385
00:14:39,480 --> 00:14:40,120
Chase him, hurry!

386
00:14:40,159 --> 00:14:40,759
Fall back faster!

387
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:42,039
Don't forget to form the defensive line!

388
00:14:44,159 --> 00:14:45,240
Changzhou!

389
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:47,120
Let's go!

390
00:14:48,480 --> 00:14:49,320
Changzhou!

391
00:14:49,360 --> 00:14:51,440
Now this is real football.

392
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:22,879
That's clearly offside!

393
00:15:23,440 --> 00:15:24,000
It's so obvious!

394
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:24,799
How is that offside?

395
00:15:24,799 --> 00:15:25,639
What do you mean offside?

396
00:15:25,960 --> 00:15:26,559
Listen to me.

397
00:15:26,559 --> 00:15:27,360
What are your ears for?

398
00:15:27,360 --> 00:15:27,960
Can't you hear there's no whistle?

399
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:28,759
Are you too far away to see?

400
00:15:28,759 --> 00:15:29,360
I'm telling you,

401
00:15:29,480 --> 00:15:30,879
even the VAR wouldn't call it.

402
00:15:31,799 --> 00:15:32,720
Changzhou and Huai'an,

403
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:34,159
do they have some kind of beef?

404
00:15:35,039 --> 00:15:36,279
The match is so intense,

405
00:15:36,720 --> 00:15:37,879
the crowd is so fired up.

406
00:15:38,759 --> 00:15:40,679
You can imagine the whole of Jiangsu

407
00:15:40,679 --> 00:15:42,000
as one big city.

408
00:15:42,679 --> 00:15:44,399
With thirteen teams inside.

409
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:46,240
So in the Jiangsu Super League,

410
00:15:46,480 --> 00:15:47,440
every single match

411
00:15:47,559 --> 00:15:48,840
is a local derby.

412
00:15:48,840 --> 00:15:49,440
I can't play football?

413
00:15:49,519 --> 00:15:50,159
Whether I can play football,

414
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:51,000
don't you know?

415
00:15:51,000 --> 00:15:51,519
I'm telling you,

416
00:15:51,519 --> 00:15:52,320
you simply can't play football.

417
00:15:52,320 --> 00:15:52,840
There's nothing more to say.

418
00:15:52,840 --> 00:15:53,879
Can you even play football?

419
00:15:54,600 --> 00:15:55,320
Interesting.

420
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:56,399
Ma,

421
00:15:56,960 --> 00:15:57,840
starting today,

422
00:15:58,360 --> 00:16:00,519
I'm a Changzhou FC fan too.

423
00:16:01,919 --> 00:16:02,480
Look at him,

424
00:16:02,799 --> 00:16:03,559
number nineteen.

425
00:16:03,759 --> 00:16:05,240
He's an employee at my company.

426
00:16:05,600 --> 00:16:06,120
An employee?

427
00:16:06,679 --> 00:16:07,279
Are you saying

428
00:16:07,399 --> 00:16:09,120
the team these tens of thousands are cheering for

429
00:16:09,480 --> 00:16:11,000
is an amateur team?

430
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:12,080
That's right.

431
00:16:14,200 --> 00:16:16,639
And our team

432
00:16:17,519 --> 00:16:18,440
hasn't won a single match

433
00:16:18,440 --> 00:16:19,200
in a very long time.

434
00:16:20,360 --> 00:16:21,960
We're all hoping for a victory.

435
00:16:23,559 --> 00:16:24,600
I'm coming back next week.

436
00:16:25,080 --> 00:16:25,840
Great, you're welcome anytime.

437
00:16:26,360 --> 00:16:27,320
Go team!

438
00:16:34,279 --> 00:16:36,919
Huai'an and Changzhou finished 0-0,

439
00:16:36,919 --> 00:16:38,159
ending in a draw.

440
00:16:38,360 --> 00:16:39,799
Changzhou FC has finally earned

441
00:16:39,799 --> 00:16:41,919
their first point of the season.

442
00:16:42,360 --> 00:16:44,840
We look forward to seeing both teams

443
00:16:45,080 --> 00:16:47,559
perform even better in upcoming matches.

444
00:17:04,079 --> 00:17:04,720
Stop studying it.

445
00:17:05,079 --> 00:17:06,039
Come, have some tea.

446
00:17:17,599 --> 00:17:18,160
Senior,

447
00:17:18,759 --> 00:17:20,079
we've played football for so many years,

448
00:17:21,440 --> 00:17:22,279
when have I ever seen you

449
00:17:22,279 --> 00:17:23,279
this worked up?

450
00:17:24,079 --> 00:17:24,839
You seemed just now

451
00:17:24,839 --> 00:17:25,759
even more anxious than me.

452
00:17:26,039 --> 00:17:27,480
How could I not be?

453
00:17:28,319 --> 00:17:29,079
In the Jiangsu Super League now,

454
00:17:29,119 --> 00:17:30,480
everyone fears you Thirteen-Nil.

455
00:17:31,519 --> 00:17:32,200
The moment you

456
00:17:32,200 --> 00:17:33,240
take points off anyone,

457
00:17:33,559 --> 00:17:34,680
they get nailed straight onto

458
00:17:34,720 --> 00:17:36,039
the Jiangsu Super League's pillar of shame.

459
00:17:36,480 --> 00:17:37,480
Hasn't your Huai'an team

460
00:17:37,799 --> 00:17:38,559
also turned the Jiangsu Super League

461
00:17:38,559 --> 00:17:39,559
upside down?

462
00:17:40,240 --> 00:17:41,599
Otherwise, where did the name

463
00:17:41,720 --> 00:17:42,279
"Wave-Riding Stallion" come from?

464
00:17:43,240 --> 00:17:44,839
As they say, strong against the strong,

465
00:17:45,200 --> 00:17:46,039
unpredictable against the weak.

466
00:17:46,599 --> 00:17:47,400
After playing you,

467
00:17:48,240 --> 00:17:48,920
that's been confirmed.

468
00:17:49,359 --> 00:17:50,759
Still better than us.

469
00:17:52,119 --> 00:17:53,000
They call it a friendly,

470
00:17:53,920 --> 00:17:54,799
but on the pitch,

471
00:17:55,240 --> 00:17:56,240
it's an all-out war.

472
00:17:57,480 --> 00:17:58,119
By the way, Senior,

473
00:17:58,519 --> 00:17:59,480
do you remember what Master

474
00:17:59,480 --> 00:18:00,480
once said to us?

475
00:18:01,440 --> 00:18:02,079
Friendship

476
00:18:02,559 --> 00:18:04,119
is also earned through true skill.

477
00:18:06,599 --> 00:18:08,160
That's the charm of the Jiangsu Super League.

478
00:18:09,480 --> 00:18:10,519
Thirteen cities,

479
00:18:10,960 --> 00:18:12,519
just like thirteen brothers,

480
00:18:13,519 --> 00:18:15,240
all giving everything

481
00:18:15,519 --> 00:18:16,319
for their hometown's honor.

482
00:18:17,279 --> 00:18:18,119
At the end of the day,

483
00:18:19,039 --> 00:18:19,880
we're still one family.
